sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_064_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Data Transfer to a Central System
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System does not support DataTransfer for a specific vendorId

    CP->>CS: 1. DataTransfer.req
    Note right of CP: vendorId: <Unsupported VendorId><br/>messageId: (optional)<br/>data: (optional)

    CS-->>CP: 2. DataTransfer.conf
    Note left of CS: status: Rejected OR UnknownMessageId<br/>OR UnknownVendorId

    Note over CP,CS: Note: status Accepted is allowed,<br/>but vendor should be warned about this behaviour
    Note over CS: Validation: Central System does not<br/>accept the DataTransfer.req
